                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Isaac Ostland</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="ostlandI" start="1054.174" end="x">There were three of us. And we too for various reasons were forced to become separated, due to the difficulties with transportation. It was prohibited to travel from one place to another and that is how we became separated.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
