            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="ostlandI" start="1151.867" end="x">I was occupied in all kind of labor. I had to work in a kolhkhoz, I had to work in a labor gang, over water, fishing, floating logs . . .</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="boderD" start="1162.661" end="x">H-um.</span>
