            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Isaac Ostland</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="ostlandI" start="1232.915" end="x">I kept my beard all the time [that of course could not be of great importance in Russia where most of the peasants wear long beards].</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
