                Tel&#197;iai Ghetto
            </p>
                                    <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Tel&#197;iai, Lithuania<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                This ghetto was established in late August 1941 and contained Jewish women and children from the surrounding area (their men had already been massacred).  The ghetto was liquidated in December 1941 with the murder of the women and children.
            </div>
